{"data":[{"id":559669924,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559669924","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545749906,"updated_time":1545751351,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e十七岁谁还不是觉得自己很牛逼啊，射了还能硬的年纪，真好。看天底下谁都不服，老子天下第一\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559647303,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559647303","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545747776,"updated_time":1545747776,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e骚年，你知道自己在说什么吗？虽然丘成桐老师觉得哥猜没那么重要（我并不这么认为)但哥猜肯定是个难题是没问题的，最后能解决这个问题的也肯定是个很厉害的数学家。哪怕只凭这个拿不了菲尔兹奖，拿个数论界的Cole奖还是没问题的。而且就我所知清华的一个数学教授(不知道是不是做数论的）也是花了半年还是一年才理解陈景润那个1+2的2页简化版本的一页。这就已经是清华的教授了，况且陈也没最后解决这个问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e    很年轻就能做出现代数学上的大工作的就我所知最年轻的应该是Drinfeld20岁就出版的论文“elliptic module”（1974）确实是个超级大结果。可能是他19岁的时候和Yurimanin一起搞的，他也是15岁就IMO满分了，当时是最年轻的满分。还有数学大师阿诺尔德本科的时候证明了希尔伯特23个问题里的一个。然后就是KONTSEVICH研究生第一年就有了解Witten conjecture的思路，研二彻底的解决了，Donaldson也是博士第二年解决了对角化定理。这都是他们拿菲奖的结果。解决了庞加莱猜想的佩雷尔曼大概也是到了博士毕业才解决了灵魂猜想。以上都是当代数学的名宿了。高中生解决哥猜不要是上清华北大，直接把你当国宝供起来都可以了吧\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559588518,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"228d3ec83706a325be682246a5676ac5","url_token":"feng-lai-fan-yi-guo-qian-li-wai","name":"风来帆已过千里外","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-17336a901fa4daa62c902c0c2c5c8be9_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-17336a901fa4daa62c902c0c2c5c8be9_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/228d3ec83706a325be682246a5676ac5","user_type":"people","headline":"等风来  帆来吗?","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559588518","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545741777,"updated_time":1545741777,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e从今天到1.1  我姑且认为你是在整理你写的东西.但这不应该发表在知乎上.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e历史上（一般n大于等于5次）方程的解这个问题也很著名，被欧拉和拉格朗日等一系列大牛研究过（但没结果），当时也有民科鲁菲尼，但他的论文在他活着的时候没得到重视.~~~~~~直到天才伽罗瓦建立群论证明方程无解结束。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想大牛们不会在知乎上问做什么能去什么好大学，他们本来就能去。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在1.1发出来前，我认为问这个问题已经比‘我三模300，请问能上清北吗’更无语.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559586797,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"92df02140d8bda3edffb0cba1674119c","url_token":"da-xue-hun-ri-zi","name":"学渣级人士","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/92df02140d8bda3edffb0cba1674119c","user_type":"people","headline":"宝剑锋从磨砺出，梅花香自苦寒来","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559586797","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545741595,"updated_time":1545838328,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e 你们都被题主涮了，我认为他是吸引关注度或者搞商业炒作要不就是要钓鱼收集什么，还有不用学数学专业都能分析出楼主绝对不是有能力证明出哥德巴赫猜想的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e        你都那么牛了思想层次还停留在把上个名校本科当最高追求的程度？恐怕最次也得评个教授去教清华北大学生了吧！这就是最大的不合理。说到怎么上清北方法多了有当外国人的，有高考移民的，有改民族的，有竞赛作弊的，有论文造假的,有高考舞弊的，有找关系的等等不一而足，但只有你独树一帜啊！不过我个人认为用论证哥德巴赫猜想的方式来保送清华北大绝对是希望最渺小的方式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e          最后我还很好奇一月一日题主准备怎么自圆其说，就是既不出丑又能让大家无话可说的收场，如果能办到这点也真是罕见的人才啊！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559513662,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559513662","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545734328,"updated_time":1546094150,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003ch1\u003e如果高中生发布了一个钓鱼问题，并因此获取了20K+的关注，会被清华北大新闻系保送吗？\u003c/h1\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/307400647\" class=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttps://www.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003ezhihu.com/question/3074\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e00647\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559470347,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559470347","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545729731,"updated_time":1545736237,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果题主真的证明出哥德巴赫猜想，那将在数学史上留下色彩浓厚的一笔。（前提是得到专家们的认可)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e保送清北是不大可能了，直接会被大佬机构预定，会满足你合理的条件\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e…………………………………………………………………………\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e作为某二本院校（拉低知乎平均学历）应用数学专业狗，从理论上来说，这不大可能，但从个人情感来说，我希望这是真的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e等明年1月1号\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559456561,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d19d4457a7e3dba41a0a0cdbdeed4544","url_token":"san-yue-de-jiu","name":"鱼沉","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-91c6e74032aab55a7e2609634b8956b8_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-91c6e74032aab55a7e2609634b8956b8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d19d4457a7e3dba41a0a0cdbdeed4544","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559456561","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545728444,"updated_time":1545728444,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e都这样了还上什么大学啊\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":557840470,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5d036f5b9dccbb2dac642cb9a3292bb5","url_token":"luo-mo-34-80","name":"罗莫","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2f1c2342ee81ea2d8eae0cfc6db6569e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2f1c2342ee81ea2d8eae0cfc6db6569e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5d036f5b9dccbb2dac642cb9a3292bb5","user_type":"people","headline":"心开者，幼冲而即悟；意闭者，皓首而难精。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557840470","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545535159,"updated_time":1546248853,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e支持你选择＂如果＂，不认同你选择＂那么＂。你的＂如果＂有实现的可能，当年的伽罗华就和你一般大，但解决了当时一流的数学问题，并开创了现代数学，英雄不问出处，包括年龄。至于能不能用初等的方法解决，回答是可以的，虽不简单，有时会比高等的更难，但必有希望，一切高等都是通过初等构造出来的，别听那些给你泼冷水的人。但你的＂那么＂，的确动机没摆正，探索数学真理是为了发现更深刻的数学真理，至于如何被认可，是顺带收获，包括一流数学杂志愿发表你的论文以及今后获奖都算。你的东西被追随是别人的事，你可以不断探索出新知是你的最大成功，其他都是次要的。更不要本末倒置去追求真理，做转换手段可以，为了实现更高目屈尊卧底一下可以。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一道难题人类几百年未曾拿下，应该集体感到汗颜，一事不知，儒者之耻。凡血性之人都不会见此无动于衷。更不会去嘲讽那些挑战者，50步笑100步，多少有些依剧，绝望者笑有希望者就是100步笑50步了。天下兴亡匹夫有责，其实可改成天下兴亡我就有责，每人一样，探究前沿真理不就是关心天下兴亡吗？门槛跟学生大，中，小何干！目标跟是否为了上北大，清华何干！英雄不问出处，小孩，女子人人皆行，英雄不为去处，北清，菲奖怎算远方。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563539703,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a0d97f2b2d1fbe6b6ce4c8b09681d020","url_token":"mu-yi-97-81-36","name":"穆易","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ec713a8ac1e29df53a7306493286326e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ec713a8ac1e29df53a7306493286326e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a0d97f2b2d1fbe6b6ce4c8b09681d020","user_type":"people","headline":"共产主义者 ","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563539703","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546248235,"updated_time":1546248703,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e能，我就是证明出了黎曼猜想而被清华保送的（滑稽）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560663016,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fbf11b24b627c3dcac4639d978dd8d2c","url_token":"da-xuan-wu","name":"大玄武","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-28466fb7be04b7fb34656f13b40a2254_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-28466fb7be04b7fb34656f13b40a2254_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fbf11b24b627c3dcac4639d978dd8d2c","user_type":"people","headline":"小说作者，经济学专业","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560663016","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545877751,"updated_time":1545877751,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我觉得不管是证明还是没有证明，水平已经是在那里了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我个人觉得高中生有才华就应该向世界难题进行攻克，君不见中国历史，年轻有为者英雄辈出，对数学的热爱应该坚持。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e事实上走出社会的人都会告诉你，做自己喜欢的事业是最幸福的。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e本人数学能力一般，甚至用差形容都不为过，所以从事的是文学一类，但是对数学的重要性一直都有很深的理解。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的建议是，你可以寄出去给211大学信用比较好的大学教授过目，以他为判断和推荐，去冲击哥德巴赫猜想，失败也没有关系，你的才华一定会被重视，陈景润、华罗庚都是偏科，钱钟书大师也是偏科，人才就应该去最好的学府。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560484943,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"abc716ddf6eee50b69c4da8e90f8d0d6","url_token":"yu-sheng-de-di-yi-tian","name":"小四十一呀","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f3cb291b106cbbf2a79ba136dc7d1ef2_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f3cb291b106cbbf2a79ba136dc7d1ef2_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/abc716ddf6eee50b69c4da8e90f8d0d6","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560484943","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545841743,"updated_time":1545979590,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e这个问题争执得我的头都痛了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得这并没有有些人说的那么夸张的程度，他错了，告诉他错了就行了，我并没有觉得他侮辱了科学家侮辱了数学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果他真的是为了装逼提出了这个问题，那么现在这么多人正儿八经的把这事提出来争执，那不就达到他的目的了？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e每个人的想法不一样，我理解不了为什么你们选择这样去嘲讽他，但是看了那么多评论大概也有种模糊的概念了。在你们看来他真的那么不可理喻的话，直接忽视他难道不更好吗？如果直接不理会他他不过是个跳梁小丑根本不会有人在意他，正是因为你们这么多人正儿八经的把这事拎出来说了去争执了，才显得他说他证明出了哥德巴赫猜想这件事真的成了一件事了【不知道能不能懂我的意思orz】\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们可以选择去嘲讽他，但是在我自己看来，可以但没必要。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e--------------下面是原答案---------------\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看了一些答案，有些人在嘲讽提问者，我就emmmm，不管提问者是不是年轻气盛心高气傲还是中二病初生牛犊不怕虎，至少在很多人每天很丧的生活，每天在床上躺尸【我自己╭(°A°`)╮】的情况下，他愿意在这上面去花功夫去研究，不管结果怎么样，我觉得这是很棒的事啊。为什么偏要去嘲讽他呢？对一个高中生抱有善意很难吗？？？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不管最后他有没有证明出来，希望他能被大家温柔以待(ง •̀_•́)ง\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560186813,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"43790bc7166f65aeb49ca103f83b6855","url_token":"he-nan-88","name":"何南","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a47b0a484712d4ec368721d8660e9809_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a47b0a484712d4ec368721d8660e9809_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/43790bc7166f65aeb49ca103f83b6855","user_type":"people","headline":"云雾苍茫各一天，可怜西北起烽烟\n东来暴客西来盗，还有胡儿在眼前","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560186813","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545816388,"updated_time":1545816388,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":18,"content":"\u003cp\u003e高斯17岁尺规作正十七边形，牛顿22岁发明微积分，爱因斯坦26岁发表狭义相对论，我生的晚，这三个历史时刻都没有遇到，难道一月一日要见到人类科学史第四个伟大时刻？我好期待！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":564006276,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564006276","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546320403,"updated_time":1546320403,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"昨天看了一下证明过程……实在忍不住了……果然现在知乎只能用来开花了……但是还是给点建议吧……从4×10的18次方+2开始去找一个不是两个素数之和的偶数……应该比你在这当民科有用………还有就是，这个高中生写出了一个过程，说明他在思考，思考的人不应该像这样被民科大队批判","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562592435,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"ab2b651c629eb54e3ddccea9caef817e","url_token":"mu-shi-han-37","name":"暮湿寒","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3aca97630d87974e8320db41304aaaef_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3aca97630d87974e8320db41304aaaef_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/ab2b651c629eb54e3ddccea9caef817e","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562592435","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546105255,"updated_time":1546105286,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e所有高赞答案都没有正面回答问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主问的是高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想能否保送清北，什么题主证明不出来，清北不是最好的，什么不如当教授等等都不是这个问题的回答，所有高赞答案全都审题不清。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我来正面回答这个问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e首先，我的回答是，不能。至少是不能直接的保送，不管哥德巴赫猜想多难证，你看起来有多牛。这是因为，直接保送这不合“规矩”。据我所知，国家规定的可能有保送资格有省级优秀学生，竞赛集训队，运动员，外国语，烈士子女等。显然，证明哥德巴赫猜想不属于其中任何一类，所以答案是不能保送。如果让你在规矩之外保送，保送制度就乱了套了，比如我救人能不能保送？人命难道没个破猜想重要？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过，规矩是死的，人是活的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你的实力得到了国家的认可，国家认为有必要争取你这个人才，不让你外流，而你只要上清北。国家可以在规矩限定之内给你最大的上清北的可能。比如你数学好，那就让你参加数学竞赛，大不了提前给你泄题，组织改卷老师认你的字迹，让你轻轻松松进集训队，这样就符合规矩了。或者给你个运动员证明保送，再给你个运动员训练因公受伤的证明堵别人的口也可以符合规矩等等。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总之，规矩不能破，在规矩之内，可以全力“操作”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过，不过哥德巴赫猜想再难证，也算是理论数学范畴，这种人国家应该还没有举国争取的欲望，要是应用物理或者工程方向的国家应该会有兴趣得多。当然，清北数学系教授可能会叹服于你的水平，但是单凭教授们也操作不了太多，顶多自主招生你当哑巴交白卷也强行给你降到一本线，你还是得高考。何况现在自招那么透明，稍微被人举报教授就不用做了，我猜教授们顶多加你个好友和你交流交流，在升学方面帮不了你太多。不过有了这些资源，你不读大学混理论数学圈也没问题，大不了破格录取你当讲师，当讲师的规矩一个学校就能操作。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，答案是不行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其余的看看高赞答案，清北不是唯一出路，前提是真有人能证明。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560636087,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b22440dbdfda23b1eebaabb2f57e0fec","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560636087","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545875738,"updated_time":1545875738,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我证明出了哥猜，说到哥猜——\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e明年年初，中美合拍的西游记即将正式开机，我将继续扮演美猴王孙悟空，我会用美猴王艺术形象努力创造一个正能量的形象，文体两开花，弘扬中华文化，希望大家多多关注。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560481979,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"19ec14de345f322b6265c8f3a955863c","url_token":"qi-zhi-fa-43","name":"弃治发","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/19ec14de345f322b6265c8f3a955863c","user_type":"people","headline":"哈哈哈","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560481979","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545841453,"updated_time":1545841453,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不管是不是真的证明出来了，我感觉他也已经很优秀了，为什么评论冷嘲热讽的，鼓励鼓励不好吗？又不是做了什么坏事，还扯什么非蠢即坏，柠檬精吧。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":564029683,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564029683","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546322789,"updated_time":1546322789,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e一群无聊的人给人家小孩子的证明找茬还要备份还要瞎怼，自己心里没点数吗，不知道这肯定不可能吗？年轻中二而已，无聊瞎凑热闹还能长篇大论的人才是真闲的没事干的吃饱了撑的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563883912,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563883912","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546307371,"updated_time":1546311883,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"\u003cp\u003e有的人的嘴脸真是难看\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就好比一个中等生或者差生，声称做出来了某个难题，虽然一般以他的水平不可能做出来，事后也证明的确没能做出来。这时候某些“尖子生”就说了，连我们都没能做出来，你根本不可能做出来的，你声称做出来了就是对我的侮辱，我嘲讽你是对你好哦。可是这个中等生整个过程并没有骂人，只是个做错题目的学生，也能虚心接受自己的错误。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e整个过程中“尖子生”仗着自己学习稍微好一点就对别人的努力大加嘲讽，这种人在哪个班都不会受欢迎的吧，怎么到知乎就反过来了呢\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有的人说是要博人眼球？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e博人眼球？声称证明哥猜的多了，为什么这个人获得了异常多的关注，还不是一部分人想看笑话，明明只是一个高中生的无知，是被你们这些人硬生生的抬了上去\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这里借用三体的一句名言\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e无知和弱小不是生存的障碍，傲慢才是\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看到现在，最傲慢的就是那些看客了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有的人觉得别人一定要知道自己所知道的所谓的“常识”，不然就要嘲讽一番，那么有的人还觉得获得年薪100w的方法还是常识，就可以嘲讽你们这些傲慢的人了吗？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560178460,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e3aff81480910a369b6a47316119401d","url_token":"xin-xuan-38-82","name":"xin xuan","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e3aff81480910a369b6a47316119401d","user_type":"people","headline":"专业打字,","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560178460","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545815676,"updated_time":1545895814,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e下面一大堆人连哥德巴赫猜想,reimann zeta函数都不知道，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就开始讽刺、嘲笑题主，好像他已经知道了证明过程并且推翻了一样。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e让我想起哥白尼被迫害，伽利略被嘲笑时的无知众人，既然啥都不懂，麻烦别急着下结论，OK？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那样会显得你们很无知。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有重庆公交坠江，女司机的遭遇。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然我也不懂，但是我会保留意见。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e不过虽然我也不太相信证明是真的，但是当时不也很多人不相信哥白尼吗？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e如果有大佬表态说他的证明有误，马上删帖。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e没有的话，我等还是闭嘴吧。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560856216,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b55e51b0ff42e8cc231d21598a622f14","url_token":"dong-zhe-jian","name":"司空百味","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b77867b38e2ec03a4c5405884e3e990a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b77867b38e2ec03a4c5405884e3e990a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b55e51b0ff42e8cc231d21598a622f14","user_type":"people","headline":"想得却不可得，你奈人生何。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560856216","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545893873,"updated_time":1546282925,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不好意思，我以为你就算证不出来至少也是花了心思下了功夫的，但你这答案里的错误明显到我一文科生都看的出来。老实说你是不是看时间快到了随便写点凑数？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e终于可以说声辣鸡知乎现在的氛围还不如贴吧了，题主问的是解出来了能不能保送清华，一堆人在乎的却是他根本不可能解出来并阴阳怪气冷嘲热讽，还上升到国家教育学术层面（这中间有多少人对哥德巴赫猜想的了解还不如题主的），当然有些高赞的答主认真分析我觉得很棒。这就跟一个常年差生突然考到全级第一，所有人怀疑他是作弊的一样。仔细看看你们身边的人和你们自己的嘴脸，是不是最喜欢落井下石，通过打压来满足自己卑微的虚荣心。你从来不关心别人到底怎么样，你只想跟着群众满足口舌之快而已。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我退一万步来讲，就算一个高中生来知乎问了一个很蠢的问题，这就是你们这群“数学家”群起而攻之的理由？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不太明白，人家只是对自己的爱好抱有极大的热枕，并想用这种热枕上清华北大，只不过恰好他的爱好比较“宏伟”又广而告之了而已，各位键盘侠们又何必恶言相向冷嘲热讽呢？就算他的算法和证法出了错误，也不会影响任何人，也是受限于他的年龄而已。能对数学难题有兴趣和认真钻研本身就值得鼓励。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e任何一个努力认真的人都值得尊重。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=1300\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=1260\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2283}}
